(Guess you missed my post Logo.)
 Lunarpine listened to the conversation between Spears, Smokescreen and
Firearms.  It wasn't sounding good. if they had thier way she'd be poked,
prodded, and scanned until the Matrix came home. He felt bad for her. Maybe
a trip to the CF is what he needed. If he remembered corectly, Prowl was
stationed there. It'd be nice to see his old commander again.

"I've got a Transport pod ready for takeoff just up the hill, I could take
her with me." He didn't want to keep Veratis waiting very long but how long
could a trip to Africa take.
